<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 20:07:11 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列内政部长不顾财政部长反对向阿拉伯城镇提供资金</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/israels-interior-minister-sends-funds-to-arab-towns-over-finance-ministers-objection/0000018b-9117-d7a8-afcf-bbb749840000</link><description>8 月，极右翼宗教犹太复国主义党的财政部长贝扎莱尔·斯莫特里奇 (Bezalel Smotrich) 发誓要暂停提供资金，直到能够证实这笔钱不会落入阿拉伯犯罪分子手中。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 19:57:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/israels-interior-minister-sends-funds-to-arab-towns-over-finance-ministers-objection/0000018b-9117-d7a8-afcf-bbb749840000</guid></item><item><title>内塔亚胡既虚弱又害怕。他必须走</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-02/ty-article-opinion/.premium/nentayahu-is-weak-and-afraid-he-must-go/0000018b-9163-d477-a1ff-f763c5a60000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 19:55:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-02/ty-article-opinion/.premium/nentayahu-is-weak-and-afraid-he-must-go/0000018b-9163-d477-a1ff-f763c5a60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军主席表示，如果医院燃料耗尽，以色列将允许进入加沙；内塔尼亚胡称他不同意</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/idf-chief-israel-to-allow-fuel-into-gaza-for-hospitals-netanyahu-disputes-this/0000018b-9111-d7a8-afcf-bbb377200000</link><description>赫兹尔·哈勒维否认有关加沙医院燃料短缺的报道，承诺未来进入加沙地带的燃料将受到监控，以免到达哈马斯</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 18:44:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/idf-chief-israel-to-allow-fuel-into-gaza-for-hospitals-netanyahu-disputes-this/0000018b-9111-d7a8-afcf-bbb377200000</guid></item><item><title>“系统性的政治迫害”：加沙战争中对以色列-阿拉伯人的迫害是什么样子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/systematic-witch-hunt-what-persecution-of-israeli-arabs-looks-like-amid-gaza-war/0000018b-90db-db7e-af9b-fbdb254e0000</link><description>逮捕、审讯、解雇、大学开除——在最近一波可能撕裂以色列社会脆弱结构的事件中，阿拉伯公民成为以色列安全官员甚至他们自己同事的目标</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 18:15:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/systematic-witch-hunt-what-persecution-of-israeli-arabs-looks-like-amid-gaza-war/0000018b-90db-db7e-af9b-fbdb254e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列参加意大利漫画节引发加沙战争愤怒</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/israeli-presence-at-italian-comics-festival-draws-ire-over-gaza-war/0000018b-90e4-d7a8-afcf-bae7b9b60000</link><description>以色列兄弟阿萨夫·哈努卡 (Asaf Hanuka) 和托梅尔·哈努卡 (Tomer Hanuka) 本应在今年的卢卡漫画和游戏节上受到招待，但以色列大使馆的参与导致几位艺术家退出。最终，兄弟俩决定不参加：“我们不想从真正的战争转向媒体战争”</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 18:06:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/israeli-presence-at-italian-comics-festival-draws-ire-over-gaza-war/0000018b-90e4-d7a8-afcf-bae7b9b60000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗的“后天”困境将为真主党的下一步行动铺平道路</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/irans-day-after-dilemma-will-pave-hezbollahs-next-steps/0000018b-8cce-db71-a7df-fdcf78b80000</link><description>德黑兰正在协助哈马斯、维持其在该地区的其他立足点并避免与美国直接军事对抗</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 17:24:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/irans-day-after-dilemma-will-pave-hezbollahs-next-steps/0000018b-8cce-db71-a7df-fdcf78b80000</guid></item><item><title>“我们知道你住在哪里”：自以色列与哈马斯战争以来，瑞典犹太人感到不安全</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-11-02/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israel-hamas-war-has-shaken-swedish-jews-sense-of-security/0000018b-9081-d7a8-afcf-baa356450000</link><description>学生们呆在家里不上课或上课并遭受虐待，抗议者呼吁消灭以色列，激进的伊斯兰组织不受约束地活动。在加沙战争和大规模屠杀的背景下，瑞典犹太社区担心其安全</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 17:23:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-11-02/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israel-hamas-war-has-shaken-swedish-jews-sense-of-security/0000018b-9081-d7a8-afcf-baa356450000</guid></item><item><title>在世界各地，针对犹太人的威胁的新时代已经开始</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/around-the-world-a-new-era-of-threats-against-jews-has-begun/0000018b-90af-db71-a7df-fdef9f580000</link><description>我错误地认为从英国到美国的犹太人不再面临重大威胁。正如过去几周所表明的那样，反犹太主义依然存在，对散居海外的犹太人构成了真正的死灰复燃的威胁</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 16:40:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/around-the-world-a-new-era-of-threats-against-jews-has-begun/0000018b-90af-db71-a7df-fdef9f580000</guid></item><item><title>继哈马斯之后，国际干预是加沙唯一选择</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/this-international-intervention-in-gaza-could-be-the-first-step-toward-a-palestinian-state/0000018b-8f49-d7a8-afcf-afeb97640000</link><description>随着巴勒斯坦人向建国过渡，国际维和人员驻扎在加沙地带和约旦河西岸的概念并不新鲜，但长期以来被忽视。美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯刚刚暗示，这可能是哈马斯事件后第二天的一个选择</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 16:39:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/this-international-intervention-in-gaza-could-be-the-first-step-toward-a-palestinian-state/0000018b-8f49-d7a8-afcf-afeb97640000</guid></item><item><title>从也门向以色列发射导弹：史无前例的发射、史无前例的拦截</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/missile-from-yemen-to-israel-unprecedented-launch-unprecedented-interception/0000018b-8f88-d7a8-afcf-afab9c5e0000</link><description>伊朗本周从也门发射到埃拉特的导弹——距离至少 1,600 公里——打破了两项记录：从地面炮台发射弹道导弹的最远射程，以及以色列“箭”导弹防御系统首次对弹道导弹进行实战拦截系统</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 16:34:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/missile-from-yemen-to-israel-unprecedented-launch-unprecedented-interception/0000018b-8f88-d7a8-afcf-afab9c5e0000</guid></item><item><title>过去战争的惨痛教训为以色列与哈马斯战争的战斗提供了信息</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/bitter-lessons-of-past-wars-inform-fighting-in-israel-hamas-war/0000018b-8ccd-d7a8-afcf-aeeff4a40000</link><description>以色列南方司令部认为，哈马斯更愿意派遣小股部队，用反坦克导弹、迫击炮和狙击手火力打击以色列军队。由于加沙地带兵力密集，误伤是一个问题</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 15:51:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/bitter-lessons-of-past-wars-inform-fighting-in-israel-hamas-war/0000018b-8ccd-d7a8-afcf-aeeff4a40000</guid></item><item><title>由于司法部长莱文拒绝召开司法任命委员会，退休法官将填补以色列法院的空缺</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/retired-israeli-judges-to-fill-vacancies-as-justice-minister-refuses-to-convene-panel/0000018b-9083-d477-a1ff-f78361740000</link><description>此举得到了最高法院代理院长乌兹·沃格尔曼的同意，为任命 14 名退休法官铺平了道路</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 15:50:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/retired-israeli-judges-to-fill-vacancies-as-justice-minister-refuses-to-convene-panel/0000018b-9083-d477-a1ff-f78361740000</guid></item><item><title>安吉丽娜·朱莉猛烈抨击以色列在加沙“蓄意轰炸被困人口”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-02/ty-article/angelina-jolie-slams-israels-deliberate-bombing-of-trapped-population-in-gaza/0000018b-9021-d477-a1ff-f721c9ec0000</link><description>朱莉在 Instagram 上发帖，谴责以色列对“儿童、妇女和家庭”进行“蓄意轰炸”，这些儿童、妇女和家庭在以色列与哈马斯的战争中“被剥夺了食物、药品和人道主义援助，违反了国际法”</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 14:48:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-02/ty-article/angelina-jolie-slams-israels-deliberate-bombing-of-trapped-population-in-gaza/0000018b-9021-d477-a1ff-f721c9ec0000</guid></item><item><title>全球左派对 10 月 7 日的反应威胁到反占领的斗争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-02/ty-article-opinion/.premium/the-global-lefts-reaction-to-october-7-threatens-the-fight-against-the-occupation/0000018b-8b8d-d7a8-afcf-abaf5d670000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 14:18:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-02/ty-article-opinion/.premium/the-global-lefts-reaction-to-october-7-threatens-the-fight-against-the-occupation/0000018b-8b8d-d7a8-afcf-abaf5d670000</guid></item><item><title>艾哈迈德希望以色列人倾听加沙人的声音。随后他的23名家人被杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article-magazine/.premium/ahmed-wanted-israelis-to-listen-to-gazans-then-23-of-his-family-members-were-killed/0000018b-8fb6-db7e-af9b-eff7d71f0000</link><description>在 Facebook 页面“跨越墙”上，以色列人用希伯来语阅读加沙人的个人故事，直到最后更新：“该页面创始人的整个家庭都被炸死了。”该页面的以色列联合创始人现在表示：“我不知道我们是否能够再次建造那座桥”</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 14:01:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article-magazine/.premium/ahmed-wanted-israelis-to-listen-to-gazans-then-23-of-his-family-members-were-killed/0000018b-8fb6-db7e-af9b-eff7d71f0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯的另一个受害者：基布兹的美术馆</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-kibbutzs-art-gallery-became-another-victim-of-hamas/0000018b-3dcf-d2b8-a7db-fdefbb4a0000</link><description>在哈马斯摧毁贝埃里基布兹的过程中，恐怖分子还袭击了馆长索菲·贝尔宗·麦基及其家人。他们幸存下来，但基布兹的画廊被烧毁</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 13:37:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-kibbutzs-art-gallery-became-another-victim-of-hamas/0000018b-3dcf-d2b8-a7db-fdefbb4a0000</guid></item><item><title>互动地图描绘了哈马斯 10 月 7 日在以色列和加沙边境社区所犯下的暴行规模</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article/interactive-map-depicts-scale-of-hamas-oct-7-atrocities-on-israeli-gaza-border-communities/0000018b-8fcf-d7a8-afcf-afef4f600000</link><description>新网站“绘制大屠杀地图”允许用户点击每个受影响的以色列城镇并阅读那里发生的事情的摘要。单独的、颜色编码的点突出显示了被杀害或绑架的以色列人的位置</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 13:00:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article/interactive-map-depicts-scale-of-hamas-oct-7-atrocities-on-israeli-gaza-border-communities/0000018b-8fcf-d7a8-afcf-afef4f600000</guid></item><item><title>随着愤怒的加剧，加沙人质的家人发誓不会给予以色列政府“无限的信任”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/as-anger-grows-families-of-gaza-hostages-vow-not-to-give-israeli-govt-endless-credit/0000018b-8fb5-d477-a1ff-ffb51a020000</link><description>家属发言人表示，“家属们感到不安，因为他们感觉没有就释放人质问题进行认真的谈判”。 “如果事情继续这样下去，我们别无选择，只能加大力度”</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 12:48:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/as-anger-grows-families-of-gaza-hostages-vow-not-to-give-israeli-govt-endless-credit/0000018b-8fb5-d477-a1ff-ffb51a020000</guid></item><item><title>在鱼雷和潜艇之间：哈马斯展示无人攻击武器</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/between-a-torpedo-and-a-submarine-hamas-reveals-unmanned-attack-weapon/0000018b-8f2f-db71-a7df-ffeffda80000</link><description>专家分析了无人水面车辆的视频后得出结论，它缺乏先进的功能。它有一个重达数十公斤的战斗头和一个不允许瞄准移动物体的GPS制导系统</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 12:39:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/between-a-torpedo-and-a-submarine-hamas-reveals-unmanned-attack-weapon/0000018b-8f2f-db71-a7df-ffeffda80000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队计划招募没有以色列国防军经验的定居者来保卫极端正统的西岸定居点</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/israels-army-to-recruit-settlers-with-no-army-experience-to-guard-west-bank-settlements/0000018b-8f63-d7a8-afcf-afe3a9b00000</link><description>新兵预计将接受为期三周的加速基础训练，之后他们将武装起来并驻扎在定居点。该计划向 27 岁至 50 岁、未曾在以色列军队服役的平民开放</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 11:26:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/israels-army-to-recruit-settlers-with-no-army-experience-to-guard-west-bank-settlements/0000018b-8f63-d7a8-afcf-afe3a9b00000</guid></item></channel></rss>